message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with sound and music computing. cs.CL is also likely as it deals with natural language processing and speech recognition, which can be applied to singing evaluation. cs.MM is another possible category as it deals with multimedia and audiovisual processing. cs.IR is also possible as it deals with information retrieval, which can be applied to the metadata annotation aspect of the dataset. cs.LG is less likely but still possible as it deals with machine learning, which can be applied to the automatic singing evaluation research.
